00:06:10.279 --> 00:06:11.839
So what we've done here, I'm just

00:06:11.839 --> 00:06:14.160
going back a little bit, we're checking

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:17.959
that the column values in column D

00:06:17.959 --> 00:06:22.160
are greater than or equal to value 0, so a static value.

