00:19:15.800 --> 00:19:19.000
And really, there's lots of options in there.

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:22.040
But it's a way to check the structure of the table.

00:19:22.040 --> 00:19:23.719
There's a few specialized ones here.

00:19:23.719 --> 00:19:25.680
I'm going to go through just two more.

00:19:25.680 --> 00:19:27.160
Basically, row count match, we're

00:19:27.160 --> 00:19:29.719
