01:44:14.245 --> 01:44:19.245
It's actually more shareable with people that don't use R and don't want to see R function calls.

01:44:19.245 --> 01:44:24.245
With one function called YAML interrogate, I believe it is.

01:44:24.245 --> 01:44:29.245
